children.subject: You're saying that your friend managed to bypass over 200 people on the waitlist? What the fuck? What class standing is he/she? What section did he/she enroll in? Christ this system is fucked up.

history.content: I am declared LSCS and was put on the waitlist for CS 188 (lecture and discussion have open seats). My friend, who is also declared and enrolled an hour earlier in the same section, was not put on the waitlist. Should I expect to get moved from the waitlist into the class after some waitlist updating/processing, or will I remain on the waitlist at position 201?
history.subject: Waitlisted for CS 188
